## Architecture

```
User Browser
    ↓ https://nagios.apps.ttmtech.com
HAProxy (10.45.17.118) - SSL termination, wildcard cert *.apps.ttmtech.com
    ↓ port 80
Nginx Ingress Controller (worker nodes)
    ↓
Nagios Pod (monitoring namespace)
    ↓ port 5666 (NRPE)
Target Nodes (active checks)

Prometheus → Alertmanager → Webhook Receiver → Nagios CMD pipe (passive checks)
```

