## Kubernetes Alerts (Passive Checks via Alertmanager)

Host: `hil-rke2-cluster`

### Tier 1 — Critical

- KubeAPIServerDown
- etcdInsufficientMembers
- KubeControllerManagerDown
- KubeSchedulerDown
- KubeNodeNotReady
- KubeNodeDiskPressure
- KubeNodeMemoryPressure
- KubeNodePIDPressure
- KubePodCrashLooping
- KubeDeploymentReplicasMismatch

### Tier 2 — Warning

- KubePersistentVolumeFillingUp
- KubeCPUOvercommit
- KubeMemoryOvercommit
- KubePodNotReady
- KubeContainerWaiting
- KubeDeploymentRolloutStuck
- CoreDNSDown
- KubeProxyDown

### Tier 3 — Info

- KubePersistentVolumeErrors
- KubeJobFailed
- KubeStatefulSetReplicasMismatch

### Watchdog (Heartbeat)

- Fires every 1 minute from Prometheus
- Freshness threshold: 300 seconds
- If CRITICAL — Alertmanager or Prometheus pipeline is down

