## Alertmanager Integration

### Flow

```
Prometheus detects condition
    ↓
Alertmanager routes to webhook
    ↓
nagios-webhook pod (monitoring namespace, port 5000)
    ↓
Writes to /opt/nagios/var/rw/nagios.cmd (passive check result)
    ↓
Nagios updates service status
```

### Webhook Service

```bash
kubectl get svc nagios-webhook -n monitoring
# ClusterIP:5000
# Internal URL: http://nagios-webhook.monitoring.svc.cluster.local:5000/webhook
```

### Alertmanager Config

- `AlertmanagerConfig` CRD in `cattle-monitoring-system` namespace
- Routes alerts matching `prometheus=~"cattle-monitoring-system/.*"`
- Watchdog routed via main Alertmanager secret patch

### Check Alertmanager Status

```bash
curl -s http://10.43.218.173:9093/api/v2/status | python3 -m json.tool | grep -A5 "receiver"
curl -s http://10.43.218.173:9093/api/v2/alerts | python3 -m json.tool | grep alertname
```

