### Postfix persistence

Postfix config is saved to PVC at `/opt/nagios/etc/postfix-main.cf`  
Restored via postStart lifecycle hook on every pod restart.  
If email stops working after restart:

```bash
kubectl exec -n monitoring $NAGIOS_POD -- bash -c \
  'cp /opt/nagios/etc/postfix-main.cf /etc/postfix/main.cf && service postfix restart'
```

