> 10.42.0.0/16 covers pod CIDR — required when Nagios pod is on same worker as target node

### Key NRPE commands on nodes

```
command[check_load]=/usr/lib64/nagios/plugins/check_load -r -w 2.0,1.5,1.0 -c 4.0,3.0,2.0
command[check_disk]=/usr/lib64/nagios/plugins/check_disk -w 20% -c 10% -p /
```

### Update NRPE config on all nodes via Ansible

```bash
ansible hil_cluster -i hil-nodes.ini -b -m shell -a \
  "sed -i 's/^allowed_hosts=.*/allowed_hosts=127.0.0.1,10.45.10.171,10.45.10.172,10.45.10.173,10.45.10.174,10.42.0.0\/16/' /etc/nagios/nrpe.cfg && systemctl restart nrpe"
```

